    <item>
      <title>中国挫伤碳排放提前达峰的绿色希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-dampens-green-hopes-of-an-early-peak-in-carbon-emissions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高能源官员淡化了有关该国碳排放量已提前数年达到峰值的猜测，并于周四表示，按时实现目标仍需要“付出巨大努力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-dampens-green-hopes-of-an-early-peak-in-carbon-emissions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 03:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理在会谈录音后否认美国在太平洋警察中扮演角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/australian-pm-denies-us-role-in-pacific-police-after-talks-taped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 否认了有关美国参与新太平洋安全协议的说法，此前有人录音显示他与拜登政府一名高级官员私下讨论了该协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/australian-pm-denies-us-role-in-pacific-police-after-talks-taped</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康呼吁改革陷入困境的养老金制度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/south-korea-s-yoon-calls-for-reform-of-troubled-pension-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈正在考虑改革养老金、医疗、教育和劳工领域，他称这些改革是一项艰巨的任务，关系到国家的生存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/south-korea-s-yoon-calls-for-reform-of-troubled-pension-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国高级官员与中国领导人举行会晤以恢复安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-security-aide-to-hold-rare-meeting-with-china-army-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫高级官员杰克·沙利文在与中国高级将领的罕见会谈中表示，中美两国有责任避免竞争升级为冲突，此举打破了双边关系的另一个僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-security-aide-to-hold-rare-meeting-with-china-army-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:57:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及在地区紧张局势加剧之际向索马里运送武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/egypt-delivers-weaponry-to-somalia-amid-rising-regional-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及开始向索马里提供武器并为其军队提供训练，这加剧了非洲之角地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/egypt-delivers-weaponry-to-somalia-amid-rising-regional-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列央行称明年战争持续，降息可能性不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/bank-of-israel-holds-rate-as-rising-prices-offset-low-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列央行周三将基准利率维持在 4.5%，并表示由于加沙战争仍在继续，今年剩余时间内可能不会降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/bank-of-israel-holds-rate-as-rising-prices-offset-low-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 13:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>紧张局势加剧，以色列对西岸地区进行致命袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/israel-carries-out-west-bank-military-operation-as-tensions-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在约旦河西岸发动了大规模军事行动，以打击军方所说的恐怖活动，这是加沙战争爆发以来巴勒斯坦地区敌对行动的最新一次激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/israel-carries-out-west-bank-military-operation-as-tensions-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 10:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚考虑恢复消费税以刺激财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，马来西亚政府正考虑恢复广泛的消费税，而不是削减常用汽油的补贴，以增强财政实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/malaysia-weighs-bringing-back-consumption-tax-to-boost-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 09:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
